sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Claude
    participant SessionHook as "arckit-session.mjs<br/>(SessionStart)"
    participant ContextHook as "arckit-context.mjs<br/>(UserPromptSubmit)"
    participant PreToolUse as "validate-arc-filename.mjs<br/>(PreToolUse)"
    participant Command as "/arckit.{command}"
    participant PostToolUse as "update-manifest.mjs<br/>(PostToolUse)"
    
    User->>Claude: Start session
    Claude->>SessionHook: Trigger once
    SessionHook-->>Claude: Inject ARCKIT_VERSION<br/>Detect projects/ dir<br/>Export env vars
    
    User->>Claude: /arckit.requirements
    Claude->>ContextHook: Before command runs
    ContextHook-->>Claude: Inject project inventory<br/>List ARC-* artifacts<br/>Pre-extract metadata
    
    Claude->>Command: Execute command
    Command->>PreToolUse: Attempt Write(ARC-001-REQ-v1.0.md)
    PreToolUse-->>Command: Validate filename<br/>Zero-pad project ID<br/>Route to subdirectory
    
    Command-->>Claude: Generate document
    Claude->>PostToolUse: File written
    PostToolUse-->>Claude: Update docs/manifest.json<br/>Add to index
